cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper proposes a method for enhancing the quality of data samples generated by a GAN to speed up the early phases of the training process for RL agents. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since these fields often use RL and GANs. Additionally, the paper mentions real-time systems, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
